comment:
* Table that contains information on location data sent via call composer.
     *
     * All fields in this table require the {@link Manifest.permission#ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION}
     * permission for access.

variables.name: AUTHORITY
variables.comment: * Authority for the locations content provider.

variables.name: CONTENT_TYPE
variables.comment: * Content type for the location table.

variables.name: CONTENT_ITEM_TYPE
variables.comment: * Content type for the location entries.

variables.name: CONTENT_URI
variables.comment: * The content URI for this table
